pageProduct.name: Aussie Bodies Lo Carb Whipped Mint Choc 50g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

15g PROTEIN
0.4g SUGARS
HIGH FIBRE
No artificial colours or preservatives.

Our Pro-active Nutrition products help your shape body from the inside out. Since 1991

Product Claims: 15g PROTEIN, 0.4g SUGARS, HIGH FIBRE, No artificial colours or preservatives.

Size: 50g

Flavour: Whipped Mint-Choc

Serving Size: 50g

Servings Per Pack: 1

KEY FEATURES

• Proactive Nutrition
• Great Tasting
• Guilt-Free Indulgence
• Source of Protein

Warnings

Contains: Milk and Soy.
May Contain: Cereals Containing Gluten (Wheat, Oats), Peanuts, Tree Nuts (Almonds, Hazelnuts) and Sesame Seeds.

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Aussie Bodies® Protein Blend (31%) [Calcium Caseinate (Milk), Whey Protein Isolate (Milk), Soy Protein Isolate, Soy Protein Crisps (Soy Protein Isolate, Cocoa Powder, Tapioca Starch), Emulsifiers (Soy Lecithin, Mono- and Di-glycerides of Fatty Acids)], No Added Sugar Dark Chocolate (24%) (Cocoa Mass, Cocoa Butter, Sweeteners (Polydextrose, Erythritol, Steviol Glycosides), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Flavour), Sweetener (Polydextrose), Sweetener (Sorbitol), Humectant (Glycerol), No Added Sugar Milk Chocolate Chips (3.5%) (Sweeteners (Polydextrose, Erythritol, Monk Fruit Extract, Steviol Glycosides), Cocoa Butter, Milk Solids, Cocoa Mass, Inulin, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Flavour), Vegetable Oil, Flavours, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Natural Colours (Chlorophyll-Copper Complex, Curcumin), Peppermint Oil.

Allergen Contains: Milk| Soy

Allergen May Be Present: Oats| Sesame Seeds| Tree Nuts| Wheat

Directions

Store in a cool, dry place, below 30°C. Keep out of direct sunlight.
